# Input

```json
{
	"array": [1, 2, 3],
	"boundaryFits": ["aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa"],
	"boundaryBreaks": ["aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa"]
}

```


# Options

```json
{
  "$schema": "../../../../../../packages/@biomejs/biome/configuration_schema.json",
  "json": {
    "formatter": {
      "delimiterSpacing": true
    }
  }
}
```

